---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Tools | Kreativ Sound"
  description="The Kreativ Sound tools area is being developed as a focused browser lab. Preset Mutator is the next upcoming public release."
  canonical="https://kreativsound.com/tools/"
  activeNav="tools"
>
  <section class="card page-main product-page">
    <div class="stack">
      <div class="tools-hero tools-hero-grid">
        <div class="tools-hero-copy">
          <p class="product-kicker">Tools lab</p>
          <h1 class="page-title">One browser tool at a time.</h1>
          <p class="page-lead">Kreativ Sound is treating the tools area as a focused browser lab, not a rushed suite. Preset Mutator is the next public release and the current development priority.</p>
        </div>
        <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern product-panel-accent tools-hero-panel">
          <p class="product-section-kicker">Current direction</p>
          <h2>Focused tools, narrower promises</h2>
          <p>The public release path is being kept tight: one clear browser tool, one clear workflow, and no premature suite messaging until the next tool is ready to stand on its own.</p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="product-panel-grid product-tool-grid product-tool-grid-single">
        <section class="product-panel product-tool-card product-tool-card-coming-soon product-panel-modern product-panel-accent">
          <span class="product-tool-flow">Preset -&gt; Preset</span>
          <img class="product-tool-mark" src="/apps/presetmutator/ui/favicon.svg" width="128" height="128" alt="Preset Mutator logo" />
          <h2>Preset Mutator</h2>
          <p>Load one Vital preset, bias the mutation, and push it into new preset directions without leaving the browser.</p>
          <p class="product-tool-supporting">This is the next public tool and the one being prepared for release first.</p>
          <div class="product-actions">
            <span class="button secondary is-static">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-hourglass-half" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              Coming soon
            </span>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      <section class="product-panel product-panel-summary product-panel-modern">
        <h2>Current tools strategy</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>The public tools area is being developed as an experimental lab with one clear release at a time.</li>
          <li>Preset Mutator is the current focus and the next announced browser tool.</li>
          <li>Other audio and preset ideas stay in the background until they are clear enough to release properly.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
